.SH "DESCRIPTION"
.PP
Hardware ECC for large page chips, require OOB to be read first\&. For this ECC mode, the write_page method is re\-used from ECC_HW\&. These methods read/write ECC from the OOB area, unlike the ECC_HW_SYNDROME support with multiple ECC steps, follows the
\(lqinfix ECC\(rq
scheme and reads/writes ECC from the data area, by overwriting the NAND manufacturer bad block markings\&.
